  "story": "A deeply moving devotional hymn from the Andhra Christian tradition that meditates on the unfathomable love of Jesus. Sung in prayer meetings and evening worship services, this keerthanamu has comforted countless Telugu-speaking believers through trials and suffering, reminding them of Christ's unchanging love.",
  "lyrics": {
